au.gov.ansto.bragg.process.agent
Interface Agent

All Superinterfaces:
au.gov.ansto.bragg.base.common.All, Common, au.gov.ansto.bragg.base.common.Publisher, java.io.Serializable
All Known Subinterfaces:
PortAgent, ProcessorAgent
public interface Agent
extends Common

Agents are proxies of ports and processors.

User can use them to check status of ports and processors. Not all the ports and processors have agents. The agents are specified in the algorithm recipe xml files. Agents are observable but not controllable.
